Puppet module: role

# Written by Tom McGonagle #
# mcgonagle@gmail.com
# Google Voice (617)229-5185
# http://www.puppetll.com


DESCRIPTION:
This module installs and manages role software
Standard and extended classes are available.
Decide and customize how you want to define configation files: static files, templates, infile modifications...


USAGE:
# Standard Classes 
include role              # Install and run role with standard configurations.
include role::disable     # Disable role service.
include role::disableboot # Disable role service at boot time, but don't stop if it's running.
include role::absent      # Remove role package.

DEPENDENCIES:
